 <!-- Introduction -->
 <!-- The introduction should start as shown: -->
 <purpose>
   <p>
     This part of ISO 10303 specifies an application module for the
     representation of a schedule of costs for all or part of an AEC facility or an activity associated with an AEC facility.
   </p>
 </purpose>

 <!-- Items in scope -->
 <inscope>
   <li>the document that is the schedule of costs for all or part of an AEC facility or an activity associated with an AEC facility;</li>
   <li>the object to which a schedule of costs applies;</li>
   <li>the total cost for a schedule of costs.</li>
 </inscope>

 <!-- Items out of scope -->
 <outscope>
   <li>the contract under which an activity is performed;</li>
   <li>dates upon which payments are made or become due (Note: The Cost schedule module implements the IAI capabilities for the recording of cost schedule information).</li>


 </outscope>




